  <original-body>We should clean up two things in scaffolding that are a source of confusion to new developers (as measured by questions via IRC and elsewhere):

1) The index action in the controller should use .all instead of .find(:all)

2) The index view should use +@entities.each do |entity|+ instead of +for entity in @entities+.</original-body>
